{"tid":1564542,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你仆街喇！913和你婚 好似係狗狗聯婚","createTime":"2019-09-12T22:24:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T04:47:02.000Z","uid":292717,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"61307d268592e1dcef0f989aaabf1b8807c416d6","tid":1564542,"uid":292717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q2g8Odq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq2g8Odq.jpg&h=855c8cda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅磡海韻軒海景酒店<br />\n<br />\n由於狗狗聯婚實在太熱鬧，大家一齊去賀下月圓食下燈籠玩下月餅，又由於太近殯儀館，召喚魔法師現場幫狗公狗乸破返個地獄再加棺木一副，好讓各親朋好友送狗公狗乸最後一程<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日仲要中秋，各區開花，依隻二打六狗等做Condom啦，記得袋住支休班棍你身呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和你婚和你婚，我們一起和你婚"},{"pid":"c0c41fdae4d2ea2f653cfba49f207d09905df007","tid":1564542,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:25:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmDC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=9a83bd48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各區集合地點!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n油麻地、佐敦、尖沙咀: 梳士巴利公園(太空館附近)<br />\n荃灣、大窩口、青衣: 荃灣公園(海濱長廊)、青衣海濱長廊<br />\n葵興、葵芳、荔景: 林士德遊樂場、葵涌運動場<br />\n美孚: 嶺南之風<br />\n太子、旺角: 花墟公園<br />\n荔枝角、長沙灣: 長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗: 通州街公園<br />\n油塘、藍田: 油塘道遊樂場<br />\n將軍澳、寶琳、坑口、康城<br />\n中西區（西區、中環、金鐘、半山、山頂）<br />\n灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后、炮台山: 維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌、太古、西灣河、筲箕灣: 沿海旁<br />\n小西灣、杏花邨、柴灣: 柴灣公園<br />\n鑽石山、黃大仙: 黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘: 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n大圍、沙田、馬鞍山 : 沙田百步梯<br />\n元朗、天水圍: 天水園公園<br />\n屯門: 屯門公園<br />\n南區: 鴨利洲風之塔公園<br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子山同山頂人鏈!"},{"pid":"8f74bc59ded4255fc907182be6b5cce66a832801","tid":1564542,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:25:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"a7c263a7affc9017048eb1f7f48a650e97661148","tid":1564542,"uid":17642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:27:15.000Z","msg":"乜鳩靚仔阿蛇，一定到啦"},{"pid":"1c2ac6b9ad0572f029265486b5b30d7f6177674a","tid":1564542,"uid":4105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:32:37.000Z","msg":"中秋傳統係唔係要點白色蠟燭<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2175f43340d07583e3519639c220e5b00a23612","tid":1564542,"uid":14433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:34:14.000Z","msg":"陰司紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02daaa55c6994969d27ea6fc19d06d504bc98965","tid":1564542,"uid":42668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:35:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4df9da2517b77f88ea10554cad682273f967b0b8